results.title: Invincible Iron Man #501
results.description:
Why should Tony Stark be the one to benefit from all of his technology? What right does Stark have to keep his miracles
to himself? A familiar threat in other corners of the Marvel Universe comes demanding answers- -- and salvation -- from
Iron Man. And because it's not enough to remake the world with free and limitless energy, Stark Resilient goes after the challenge of remaking another world: ASGARD.

results.title: Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #33, Deadpool Variant - Int
Thor: Heaven & Earth (2011) #4
results.description: On a train journey through the cold and forbidding Welsh countryside, an American reporter listens intently to an old man's tale of the Vikings who once invaded this land, and of the Norse Gods they summoned to protect them. But the Gods of Asgard are unprepared for what lays in wait for them - the Welsh Dragon itself, the ferocious embodiment of the land they have come to conquer. And when the Dragon takes exception to their presence, Thor, Odin, Baldur and company find they have a fight on their hands the likes of which they have never experienced.
